    "custom_liquid_QWbLRi": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .faq-section {\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n  .faq-title {\n    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n    font-style: italic;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 38px);\n    color: #c9836a;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 0 0 36px;\n  }\n  .faq-list {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .faq-item {\n    background: #faf3ef;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 18px 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-align: left;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  .faq-question span {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #222;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .faq-icon {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    color: #aaa;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: transform 0.25s ease;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n    color: #c9836a;\n  }\n  .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {\n    max-height: 300px;\n    padding: 0 20px 18px;\n  }\n  .faq-answer p {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #555;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">frequently asked questions</h2>\n  <div class=\"faq-list\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How much coverage does the Changing Foundation provide?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>The Changing Foundation offers buildable, light to medium coverage that effortlessly adapts to your needs. Start sheer for an everyday natural look, or layer for more coverage — it's completely in your control.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is the product suitable for sensitive skin?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>Yes. The Changing Foundation is dermatologist tested and formulated to be gentle on sensitive skin, including those with conditions like rosacea or vitiligo. We always recommend doing a patch test first, as individual reactions can vary.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is the Changing Foundation suitable for skin with wrinkles or fine lines?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>Absolutely. The lightweight, moisturizing formula is specifically designed to glide over fine lines and crepey skin without settling into them. It hydrates as it covers, leaving skin looking naturally smooth and even — never cakey or heavy.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>What's the best way to apply the Changing Foundation?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>For best results, apply with a brush — this helps the pigment particles blend deeper into the skin and prevents any white cast. You can also use fingers or a sponge. Start from the center of your face and blend outward in circular motions.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How does the Changing Foundation adapt its color?</span>\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <p>The formula contains encapsulated pigments that start off white. As you blend, friction and your skin's natural warmth break open those capsules, releasing warm pigment that adjusts to your unique skin tone. The result is a seamless, custom shade match — every time.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq(btn) {\n    const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  }\n</script>",
        "full_width": false,
        "show_divider": false,
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
